          <para styleclass="Popup Box">There are three types of <text styleclass="Popup Box2">joint</text> in <text styleclass="VariableName-IT" style="font-size:10pt;">MechDesigner</text><text style="font-weight:bold; font-style:italic;">:</text></para>
