          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Slide-Joint" styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">- Slide-Joint</link><image src="Red-14-2.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption">:</text> a Prismatic-Joint, (the <text styleclass="VariableName-small">P</text> Joint in a Dyad)</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
